Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.11,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{We're back.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.07,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Hey, welcome back. Thanks...}Ừm, về rồi à. Vất vả...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.82,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{What's that thing you're holding?}Cậu đang cầm cái gì thế kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.76,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Isn't it cute?}Dễ thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.04,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{It certainly is,}Ừm thì dễ thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:20.70,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{but please don't tell me \Nyou're going to keep it here.}nhưng đừng nói là tính trưng ở đây đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.96,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{May I?}Được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.85,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{I beg you, please reconsider.}Làm ơn đừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Here are the supplies we got.}Đây là nhu yếu phẩm bọn em mua.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.17,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Let me see.}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.05,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Okay, perfectly ordinary supplies.}Ồ, mua đúng rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.28,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{You're a lifesaver, Kuze.}May mà có cậu, Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.38,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Who knows what the elder Kujo would've\N done if left to her own devices?}Chứ để mỗi Kujo chị đi\N mua thì ai biết chuyện gì xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:44.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{The student council office \Nwould've become a theme park.}Hội học sinh thành cái công viên chứ gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.45,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Well, Kuze? Changed your mind \Non joining the student council yet?}Kuze, đã thay đổi quyết định chưa? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:53.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{No, though I wouldn't mind \Nhelping out occasionally.}Thôi, thỉnh thoảng ghé qua giúp thì được.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:58.32,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Then why not join on paper?}Vậy thì tham gia trên giấy tờ đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.99,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you agree with \Nbringing him on, Elder Kujo.}Kujo chị cũng tán thành à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{"On paper"? Come on now...}Trên giấy tờ gì chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{And I understand Yuki wanting me to join,}Yuki muốn em tham gia thì còn hiểu được,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{but why are you so set on bringing me on, Prez?}sao đến cả anh cũng?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:13.79,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Why are }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ so set on not joining?}Ngược lại chứ, sao cậu không muốn tham gia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:17.01,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Something tells me there's more \Nto it than all the work involved.}Có chuyện gì đó sâu xa hơn là chỉ phiền phức thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:21.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I'm not worthy of being \Na student council officer.}Em không hợp với vai trò trong hội học sinh đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.85,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{"Not worthy"? I can't say I agree.}Không hợp? Tôi không nghĩ vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:32.11,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{After all, you were a fine vice president \Nfor the middle school's student council.}Dù gì cấp 2 cậu cũng từng là hội phó hội học sinh mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:35.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That experience is what proved it to me.}Chính vì thế nên em mới chắc chắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I didn't have any suitable goals that I could\Nuse that position of power to achieve.}Bản thân em không có tham vọng\N hay mong muốn quyền lực gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.60,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{And what's wrong with that?}Vậy thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:45.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:51.00,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{I became student council president \Nto win the heart of the girl I love.}Tôi trở thành hội trưởng vì người con gái mình yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.55,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{A reason far more improper \Nthan any you may have.}Còn không phù hợp hơn cả cậu đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wait, really?}Thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.54,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Take a look at this.}Nhìn xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Is that your younger brother?}Em trai anh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.10,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{That was me back in ninth grade.}Không, là tôi hồi lớp 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?!
